24.11.2024 ~ The Beginning of Our Forever ♾️ Roka Day 🫶🏻

Yes, I believe in happy endings—because ours has just begun. I remember all the times Arun and I talked about this day, imagining how it would feel. But when the moment finally arrived, It was a whirlwind of emotions—nervousness , excitement , and overwhelmed with joy. It was a day filled with love, laughter, and countless beautiful memories—the perfect beginning to our forever. 

From dreams to reality, from two hearts to one journey. Blessed and overjoyed to start this beautiful adventure together! 💕 ♾️❤️
